ratings.question_text: What is your overall assessment of this course?

narratives.question_text: How would you summarize AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 for a fellow student? Would you recommend AFAM 505 01/AMST 643 01 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: Good choice for a student looking to get a feeling for the current status of nanomaterials fabrication and characterization from a chemical engineering perspective. An organic chemistry background recommended.
Yes, I will definitely recommend this class. It is a class focuses on an interesting aspect of Chemical E.
